// sipmesh v1 control-plane contracts.
//
// Three gRPC surfaces in this file (a fourth — Pipeline, between
// media-edge and ai-worker for streaming PCM frames — lands later):
//   Scheduler  — sip-proxy → media-server   (call allocation)
//   Edge       — media-server → media-edge   (call activation)
//   Registry   — media-edge → media-server   (register + stream events)
//
// Audio (RTP) flows UDP-direct between the SIP caller and the assigned
// media-edge; raw PCM frames between media-edge and ai-worker will use
